{"tid":842581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清潔工碼頭工作時墮海 送院搶救後不治","createTime":"2018-09-30T12:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T12:45:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41f1b876b1d5b7c207337c9691e3ddfaddfd1642","tid":842581,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"【20:01】事主送院搶救後不治<br />\n<br />\n下午2時許，一名中年清潔男工於流浮山尖鼻咀碼頭工作其間失蹤，懷疑墮海，消防及水警輪到場搜救，政府飛行服務隊亦出動直昇機搜索。至下午4時許，清潔工成功獲救後，昏迷送往醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180930/58741571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58741571&d=fDVrsvPobmzEZ9WNWW4ClP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e51ad387\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58741571&h=fb78dcad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180930/58741571</a>"},{"pid":"c6b55460c2f3fbfb91cdf40c7eb3a261c20e6c96","tid":842581,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:24:18.000Z","msg":"中年已經要做清潔 星期日都要番工<br />\n見到個天色咁靚 秋高氣爽<br />\n望到個茫茫既大海<br />\n再回望自己既人生 或者呢一刻完結係一個完美既結局"},{"pid":"8a20cf95d450ad314fa607e0fb2696c4227d83a5","tid":842581,"uid":33878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:25:48.000Z","msg":"無人捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe56515a8a149ffbc47c831de7c92383f347cfdb","tid":842581,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:27:10.000Z","msg":"返工 = ？"},{"pid":"3a330af4df07e22924e8615366296a9face9e4ff","tid":842581,"uid":95096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quot